data.name: Swarm of Rats
data.oracle_text: Swarm of Rats's power is equal to the number of Rats you control.
data.flavor_text:
"Rats, rats, rats! Hundreds, thousands, millions of them, and every one a life."
—Bram Stoker, *Dracula*
